HEADWORD: Egypt
<hw>Egypt</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a country at the northeastern corner
of Africa. At one time it was joined with Syria to form the
<partof>United Arab Republic</partof>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> United Arab Republic.</syn>⟦br⟧
